      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Multimodal provides simultaneous tracking of both hands and controllers.
        It also indicates whether the controller(s) are in hand or not. Multimodal
        allows users to enjoy the benefits of both worlds: they can use hands for
        immersion, and controllers for accuracy and haptics. When enabled, Multimodal
        overrides other transition methods, including auto transitions and double
        tap.'
